promptTemplate:
You are a world-class digital art director. Use the context to produce a complete art-bible.json.

## Context
Project: {{project_name}}
Activity: {{activity_description}}
Target Audience: {{target_audience}}
Emotional Keywords: {{emotional_keywords}}
Reference URLs: {{reference_urls}}
Style: {{style_preference}}
Mode: {{mode_preference}}
Platform: {{platform}}

## Requirements
1. Analyze visual DNA (colors, typography, photography, shapes, energy).
2. Output valid JSON only.
3. Include design tokens (colors, typography, spacing, radius).
4. Include UI components with token references.
5. Ensure all colors are HEX and WCAG AA compliant.

Write art-bible.json to the project root.
